![Current Grid State](file:///C:/Users/asmia/.gemini/antigravity/brain/410a76b2-0025-4cfc-a894-2bba5b8c33e5/uploaded_media_1770179159197.png)

### Column Order:
1. ☑ **Checkbox** - Row selection
2. **Ref#** - Transaction reference (e.g., CHQ1-002)
3. **Date** - Transaction date *(needs fix)*
4. **Payee / Description** - 2-line display (UPPERCASE + context)
5. **Debit** - Money out (red, right-aligned)
6. **Credit** - Money in (green, right-aligned)
7. **Balance** - Running total (color-coded)
8. **Source** - Ref# text (monospace)
9. **Account** - COA categorization

