## Known Issues

### 1. Date Parsing
**Issue**: Dates showing as "(No Date)" instead of actual dates.

**Root Cause**: Date field values may not be in correct format for Luxon parser.

**Next Steps**: 
- Verify date format in [ledger.core.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js)
- Ensure dates are stored as ISO strings or valid date objects
- Test with actual 2023 bank statement data

### 2. Missing 4-Card Layout
**Status**: Not yet implemented.

**Required Cards**:
